Title: An Act Changing the Name of the Liberty Elementary School in Barangay Visayan Village, in the Municipality of Tagum, Province of Davao, to Visayan Village Elementary School
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 823
An Act Changing the Name of the Liberty Elementary School in Barangay Visayan Village, in the Municipality of Tagum, Province of Davao, to Visayan Village Elementary School
Section 1. The name of the Liberty Elementary School in the Visayan Village, in the Municipality of Tagum, Province of Davao, is hereby changed to Visayan Village Elementary School.
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Approved: April 27, 1984
